Q ) write algorithm on calculate power of a number 20 .

Algorithm :

first take a number let us say A .
take power  as 0 .
calculate the power of A (i.e) A * A . and store in power .
print the power .


Q ) write algorithm on to prepare upma .

Algorithm : 

first put one kadai on the stove.
second add some oil, onions, chillis, tomatos , some salt and water.
third after boiling water add some rava in the kadai.
fourth cover the plate to kadai and reduce flame to low. 
fifth after 2 mints switch off the stove . and upma is ready.